# Secure Deployment Runner — Environment Variables
#
# This application is designed for fully offline operation.
# No environment variables are required to run or build the app.
#
# All dependencies are bundled at build time via Vite.
# No external API keys, CDN scripts, or telemetry are used.
#
# Copy this file to .env.local if you need to override build settings:
#   cp .env.example .env.local
#
# Available Vite build variables (optional):
# VITE_APP_VERSION=0.1.0    Override the displayed app version
# VITE_BUILD_DATE=2026-04-06  Override the displayed build date
